Package: hierGSEA
Title: Hierarchy-Aware Post-Processing for GSEA Results
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
        given = "Max",
        family = "Ullrich",
        role = c("aut", "cre"),
        email = "max@example.com"
    )
    )
Description: Post-processes Gene Set Enrichment Analysis (GSEA) results
    generated by 'clusterProfiler' and 'ReactomePA' while respecting the
    hierarchical structure of Reactome, Gene Ontology, and MitoCarta
    MitoPathways. The package provides hierarchy-aware filtering, family-wise
    Benjamini-Hochberg correction, significant branch ordering, and left-side
    hierarchy plotting without re-implementing the underlying enrichment
    methods.
